TITLE: Testing REST API with Jest and SuperTest
DESCRIPTION: Example of testing a REST API endpoint using Jest, SuperTest, and PlatformTest.bootstrap() to set up the server for integration testing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tsedio/tsed/blob/production/docs/docs/testing.md#2025-04-16_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: typescript
