TITLE: Importing and Transforming Team Members Data in Vue
DESCRIPTION: This script imports team data from a JSON file and transforms it into a format suitable for the VPTeamMembers component. It maps each team member's information including avatar, name, title, and social links (GitHub and Twitter).
SOURCE: https://github.com/tsedio/tsed/blob/production/docs/more/team.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: vue
CODE:
```
<script setup>
import { VPTeamMembers } from 'vitepress/theme';
import team from '../team.json';

const members = team.map((member) => {
   return {
     avatar: member.src,
     name: member.title,
     title: member.role + ' - ' + member.job,
     links: [
        { icon: 'github', link: 'https://github.com/' + member.github },
        member.twitter && { icon: 'twitter', link: 'https://x.com/' + member.twitter }
     ].filter(Boolean)
   }
})
</script>
```

